{"tid":806701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個iphone實用小技巧","createTime":"2018-09-05T02:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T02:10:14.000Z","uid":179469,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1fbf5d3544aa2f0d20ad1f8e8deae20e6fb7308d","tid":806701,"uid":179469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"唔知大家知唔知，將apps由一頁拖去另一頁，一般做法是把apps拖到螢幕邊佢會自動跳，但有時感應不好明明拖到邊位，頁面也不換。<br />\n<br />\n技巧就是，用一隻手指按住個app, 不用拖，你拎多隻手指出來由左到右或由右到左換頁，再放番原本隻手指便可<br />\n<br />\n當然用itune也簡單，但要駁電腦。"},{"pid":"94aaf17be6e8097439a17c9a10faffc52530a4e1","tid":806701,"uid":171800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:08:41.000Z","msg":"wifi斷線果陣，由底向上拉出快捷列，關&amp;開wifi就可以解決99.99%wifi問題。"},{"pid":"ac69dad8dbd57987cd7c9f359b2ef43ec89aee2e","tid":806701,"uid":171800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94aaf17be6e8097439a17c9a10faffc52530a4e1","tid":806701,"uid":171800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:08:41.000Z","msg":"wifi斷線果陣，由底向上拉出快捷列，關&amp;開wifi就可以解決99.99%wifi問題。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:10:14.000Z","msg":"其他牌子嘅垃圾機通常要重開router或打俾電訊商，iphone NO1~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}